hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I quite like cooking kamsons pharmacy failsworth Kitty sought the complaints department, but talk with it went round in circles. She was accused of “intimidating the staff” and “coming in here and feeding your mother” (the latter accusation was undeniably true). She searched for the “top man”. He is Dr Frank Harsent, the chief executive, who, according to a published list, is the 24th best-paid person in the NHS; but he works in Cheltenham, and was unavailable.
